<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
    xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Renaming elements</title>
    <para>
        Understandability can often by significantly improved by renaming elements (e.g. contracts, classes, services and attributes)
        to more intuitive and descriptive names. One should take care not to use abbreviations excessively.
    </para>
